《'''嗨翻酷暑'''》（{{lang-en|"Cool for the Summer"}}）是美国女歌手[[黛米·洛瓦托|黛米·洛瓦托]]的歌曲，作为其第五张录音室《{{le| 玩美自信 (专辑)|Confident (album)| 玩美自信}}》（2015）的首发单曲<ref>{{cite news|title=Demi Lovato Returns With Summer Anthem "Cool for the Summer"|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/demi-lovato-returns-with-summer-anthem-cool-for-the-summer-300107325.html|accessdate=2015-07-04|work=PR Newswire|date=2015-07-01|format=Press release|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805203434/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/demi-lovato-returns-with-summer-anthem-cool-for-the-summer-300107325.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Demi Lovato Recruited A Ton Of Celeb BFFs To Reveal Her Album Track List|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2252362/demi-lovato-new-album-track-list/|work=MTV|accessdate=2015-08-27|last1=Roth|first1=Madeline|date=2015-08-26|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108110457/http://www.mtv.com/news/2252362/demi-lovato-new-album-track-list/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，于2015年7月1日由[[好莱坞唱片|好莱坞唱片]]和[[小岛唱片|小岛唱片]]发行，同日透过[[聯眾唱片|聯眾唱片]]在电台首播<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Rosen|first1=Christopher|title=Demi Lovato's new single is 'Cool for the Summer'|journal=Entertainment Weekly|date=2015-06-25|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/06/25/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer|accessdate=2015-07-01|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809213628/https://ew.com/article/2015/06/25/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.republicplaybook.com/track/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer/|title=Demi Lovato "Cool for the Summer"|publisher=Republic Records|accessdate=2015-07-05|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924090134/http://www.republicplaybook.com/track/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该曲由洛瓦托、[[马克斯·马丁|马克斯·马丁]]、阿里·帕雅米（{{lang|en|Ali Payami}}）和{{le|亚历山大·埃里克·柯兰伦德|Alexander Kronlund}}共同创作<ref>{{cite web|title=Cool for the Summer|url=http://se.warnerchappell.com/song-details/WW010499884000|publisher=Warner/Chappell Music|accessdate=2015-07-01|archive-date=2015-07-05|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150705173725/http://se.warnerchappell.com/song-details/WW010499884000|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲凭借{{le|双性恋口味|Bi-curious}}和性暗示的歌词吸引关注<ref name="vulture1"/><ref name="timemag"/>。

该曲获得音乐评论家的正面评价，洛瓦托的 玩美自信和歌曲娴熟的制作受到称赞<ref name="billb"/><ref name="idolator"/>。歌曲于2015年7月18日以第36位亮相[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]]，首周售出108000张<ref name="billboard debut">{{cite news|last1=Trust|first1=Gary|title=Hot 100 Chart Moves: Rihanna Roars to New High After 'Money' Video Release|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6627221/hot-100-chart-moves-rihanna-bbhmm-video|accessdate=2015-08-24|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=2015-07-10|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129062632/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6627221/hot-100-chart-moves-rihanna-bbhmm-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年8月15日，歌曲进入百强榜前20位，位列第11<ref>{{cite web|title=Music: Top 100 Songs {{!}} Billboard Hot 100 Chart|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100/2015-08-15|website=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=2015-08-25|archive-date=2019-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902041307/https://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100/2015-08-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲也在澳大利亚和加拿大等国的国际单曲排行榜中跻身前20位，在新西兰和英国杀入前十。

