歌曲由洛瓦托、{{le|亚历山大·埃里克·柯兰伦德|Alexander Kronlund}}、[[沙凡·科提查|沙凡·科提查]]、阿里·帕雅米和[[马克斯·马丁|马克斯·马丁]]创作，帕雅米和马丁制作<ref name="nylon"/>。该曲是一首流行<ref name="nylon"/><ref name="digitalspy">{{cite web|last1=Corner|first1=Lewis|last2=Davidson|first2=Amy|title=Playlist: 10 tracks you need to hear – Robyn, Demi Lovato, Ella Eyre|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/music/feature/a655724/playlist-10-tracks-you-need-to-hear-robyn-demi-lovato-ella-eyre.html#~piNFkbEh8ZzPD0|publisher=Digital Spy|date=2015-06-30|accessdate=2015-07-18|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924043045/http://www.digitalspy.com/music/feature/a655724/playlist-10-tracks-you-need-to-hear-robyn-demi-lovato-ella-eyre.html#~piNFkbEh8ZzPD0|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[流行摇滚|摇滚]]乐<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/demi-lovato-debuts-new-single-cool-for-the-summer-listen__9947/|title=Listen to Demi Lovato's new single Cool for the Summer|work=officialcharts.com|accessdate=2016-06-14|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612142316/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/demi-lovato-debuts-new-single-cool-for-the-summer-listen__9947/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ryan Seacrest">{{cite web|url=http://www.ryanseacrest.com/2015/06/26/demi-lovato-teases-new-pop-rock-single-cool-for-the-summer-listen/|title=Demi Lovato Teases New Pop-Rock Single 'Cool for the Summer': Listen|work=Ryan Seacrest|accessdate=2016-06-14|archive-date=2015-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627191644/http://www.ryanseacrest.com/2015/06/26/demi-lovato-teases-new-pop-rock-single-cool-for-the-summer-listen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，兼有[[摇滚|摇滚]]的锐度和[[电子乐|电子]]编曲<ref name="Ryan Seacrest"/><ref>{{cite news | url=http://time.com/3968499/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer-cahill-remix/ | work=Time | first=Nolan | last=Feeney | title=Demi Lovato's 'Cool for the Summer' Gets a Remix from Cahill | date=2015-07-23 | accessdate=2016-06-14 | archive-date=2020-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924055132/https://time.com/3968499/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer-cahill-remix/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，加入了电子合成器节拍<ref name="idolator"/><ref name="nylon"/>和电音吉他的即兴重复<ref name="billb"/>。凭借这首歌曲，洛瓦托回归她的流行摇滚乐根基<ref name="fuse"/>，同时借助挑衅性的主题为自己开辟新天地。从主题上看，歌曲是关于炎夏期间与一位女情人进行性试验的。据称该曲的性暗示比洛瓦托以前的作品还要多，相比之下超越[[凯蒂·佩里|凯蒂·佩里]]的歌曲《[[亲了一个拉拉|亲了一个拉拉]]》。[[合众国际社|合众国际社]]的泰拉杰内·奥利斯马（{{lang|en|Tharadjyne Orisma}}）指出歌曲“提出了一些非常儿童不宜的建议”。歌曲的氛围音乐制作由开场的钢琴旋律及紧随其后的在副歌中伴以吉他即兴重复的嗡嗡声的合成节拍组成。其制作据称标志着洛瓦托继2011年R&B题材专辑《[[坚固柔情_(黛咪·洛瓦托专辑)|坚固柔情]]》和2013年{{le|泡泡糖流行乐|Bubblegum pop}}《[[黛咪_(专辑)|黛咪]]》后，回归她最早期录音作品的流行摇滚风格。歌曲每分钟114拍，属小快板<ref name="billb"/><ref name="fuse">{{cite web|last1=Benjamin|first1=Jeff|title=Demi Lovato Preps "Provocative," "Rock-Pop" Songs for Fall Album|url=http://www.fuse.tv/2015/06/demi-lovato-new-album|publisher=Fuse|date=2015-07-01|accessdate=2015-07-18|archive-date=2017-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170201082405/http://www.fuse.tv/2015/06/demi-lovato-new-album|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="usatoday">{{cite news|last1=Carey-Mahoney|first1=Ryan|last2=Mansfield|first2=Brian|last3=Ryan|first3=Patrick|title=Listen to these 6 songs you might've missed this week|url=http://entertainthis.usatoday.com/2015/07/03/listen-to-these-6-songs-you-mightve-missed-this-week/|publisher=USA Today|date=2015-07-01|accessdate=2015-07-18|archive-date=2016-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160101143216/http://entertainthis.usatoday.com/2015/07/03/listen-to-these-6-songs-you-mightve-missed-this-week/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 发行 ==
洛瓦托于2015年6月25日透过[[Twitter|Twitter]]宣布发行该曲，公布了单曲的封面和发行日期7月1日。{{le|MTV News|MTV News}}的艾米莉·林德娜（{{lang|en|Emilee Linder}}）评论封面：“歌曲的封面展现出穿着条纹装和人造皮革的黛咪斜视我们。她释放出一个一望而知的、居高临下的气氛，毫不关心地甩着她的太阳镜<ref name="teaser">{{cite web|last=Lindner|first=Emilee|title=Demi Lovato's New Song Teaser Gets Naughty: 'Don't Tell Your Mother'|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2197850/demi-lovato-cool-for-summer-teaser/|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2015-07-01|date=2015-06-26|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115220820/http://www.mtv.com/news/2197850/demi-lovato-cool-for-summer-teaser/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

尽管定于7月1日首发，歌曲却在正式发行一天前被泄露<ref name="nylon">{{cite web|last=Gharnit|first=Yasmeen|title=Listen To Demi Lovato's New Song "Cool for the Summer"|url=http://www.nylon.com/articles/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer|work=Nylon|accessdate=2015-07-01|date=2015-06-30|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322035825/http://www.nylon.com/articles/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。发行次日，洛瓦斯被指控抄袭[[洁西·J|洁西·J]]的《{{le|多米诺 (歌曲)|Domino (Jessie J song)|多米诺}}》和[[凯蒂·佩里|凯蒂·佩里]]的《[[亲了一个拉拉|亲了一个拉拉]]》，其中歌词“没关系的/我也有点小好奇/告诉我这是对的/还是错的/可我不在意......浅尝樱桃的滋味/我只想轻咬一口”（{{lang|en|It's okay/I'm a little curious too/Tell me if it's wrong/If it's right/I don't care ... Got a taste for the cherry/I just need to take a bite}}）跟同样由马克斯·马丁共同创作的凯蒂的《亲了一个拉拉》有异曲同工之妙<ref>{{cite news|last1=Adejobi|first1=Alicia|title=Demi Lovato denies new single Cool for the Summer is a rip-off of Katy Perry's I Kissed A Girl|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/demi-lovato-denies-ripping-off-katy-perry-song-i-kissed-girl-new-single-cool-summer-1508964|work=International Business Times|date=2015-07-02|accessdate=2015-07-05|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811163513/https://www.ibtimes.co.uk/demi-lovato-denies-ripping-off-katy-perry-song-i-kissed-girl-new-single-cool-summer-1508964|dead-url=no}}</ref>。洛瓦托则回应称歌曲听上去一点也不相似，“我认为不止一位女艺人像这样亲了一位女士”<ref name=Accusations>{{cite web|last1=Frere|first1=Jackie|title=Demi Lovato Defends New Single: 'Cool for the Summer' Sounds 'Nothing Like' Jessie J or Katy Perry|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6613312/demi-lovato-cool-summer-jessie-j-katy-perry|publisher=Billboard.com|date=2015-07-01|accessdate=2015-07-05|archive-date=2019-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421202030/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6613312/demi-lovato-cool-summer-jessie-j-katy-perry|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 专业评价 ==
歌曲获得音乐评论家的好评。《[[Nylon|Nylon]]》的雅思米恩·佳尼特（{{lang|en|Yasmeen Gharnit}}）称歌曲是一首带有“热闹、戏剧性的器乐和合成器节拍”的“耀眼地夏日的歌曲”，有别于“一些坦白的中学私人日记式歌词”<ref name="nylon"/>。《[[公告牌_(杂志)|公告牌]]》的杰森·利普舒茨（{{lang|en|Jason Lipshutz}}）给予歌曲四星评价（满分五星），称它是洛瓦托“迄今为止最 玩美自信的声明”<ref name="billb">{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/review/6613222/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer-single-review|first=Jason|last=Lipshutz|date=2015-07-01|accessdate=2015-07-01|title=Demi Lovato Gets Aggressive on Red-Hot 'Cool for the Summer': Single Review|journal=Billboard|archive-date=2020-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612161303/https://www.billboard.com/articles/review/6613222/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer-single-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|Idolator|Idolator (website)}}给出7.5分（满分10分），写道：“从细致入微的制作过程到言不由衷的歌词，只听一遍《嗨翻酷暑》便知道它将成为佳作<ref name="idolator">{{cite web|url=http://www.idolator.com/7598852/pop-perspective-demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer|title=Pop Perspective: Demi Lovato's 'Cool For The Summer' Reviewed And Rated By Idolator Editors|date=2015-07-01|accessdate=2015-07-01|publisher=Idolator}}</ref>。”《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》的诺兰·菲尼（{{lang|en|Nolan Feeney}}）表示：“洛瓦托撩人的割喉和制作人马克斯·马丁的点石成金触感将歌曲空调般的合成器熔化成一根烫嘴、坚硬的香肠<ref name="timemag">{{cite journal|url=http://time.com/3943064/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer|journal=Time|title=Demi Lovato's New Song 'Cool for the Summer' Is Seriously Hot|date=2015-07-01|accessdate=2015-07-01|first=Nolan|last=Feeney|archive-date=2018-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181031224858/http://time.com/3943064/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《[[纽约_(杂志)|纽约]]》作家迪伊·洛基特（{{lang|en|Dee Lockett}}）称其“可能是史上制作得最完美的夏日歌曲”<ref name="vulture1">{{cite web|last1=Lockett|first1=Dee|title=It's Physically Impossible to Watch Demi Lovato's 'Cool for the Summer' Video and Actually Stay Cool|url=http://www.vulture.com/2015/07/watch-demi-lovatos-cool-for-the-summer-video.html?mid=facebook_vulture|website=New York|accessdate=2015-07-24|date=2015-07-23|archive-date=2018-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181103091903/http://www.vulture.com/2015/07/watch-demi-lovatos-cool-for-the-summer-video.html?mid=facebook_vulture|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

