音乐录影带由{{le|汉娜·卢克斯·戴维斯|Hannah Lux Davis}}导演，2015年7月23日在[[Vevo|Vevo]]发布<ref>{{cite journal|first=Jessie|last=Morris|title=Demi Lovato Drops Her New Video for 'Cool for the Summer'|url=http://www.complex.com/music/2015/07/demi-lovato-new-viedo-cool-for-the-summer|magazine=Complex|accessdate=2015-07-23|date=2015-07-23|journal=|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920140721/https://www.complex.com/music/2015/07/demi-lovato-new-viedo-cool-for-the-summer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[MTV|MTV]]的克里斯蒂娜·加里波第（{{lang|en|Christina Garibaldi}}）称录影带“养眼，前卫，性感到冒烟”，指出录影带标志着“她职业生涯的新篇章，因为她散发出我们还没有见到过的 玩美自信和性感<ref>{{cite web|last1=Garibaldi|first1=Christina|title=Demi Lovato Is Sexier Than Ever in Her 'Cool for the Summer' Video: Watch|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2221649/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer-video/|publisher=MTV|accessdate=2015-07-23|date=2015-07-23|archive-date=2019-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190709053751/http://www.mtv.com/news/2221649/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer-video/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”{{le|Idolator|Idolator (website)}}的比安卡·格雷西（{{lang|en|Bianca Gracie}}）和[[数码间谍|数码间谍]]的路易斯·康纳（{{lang|en|Lewis Corner}}）都认为是洛瓦托“最色情的作品”<ref>{{cite web|last1=Gracie|first1=Bianca|title=Demi Lovato's "Cool for the Summer" Video Is A Steamy, Lady-Filled Romp: Watch|url=http://www.idolator.com/7601689/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer-video-steamy-lady-filled-romp-sexy-watch|publisher=Idolator|accessdate=2015-07-23|date=2015-07-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Corner|first1=Lewis|title=Demi Lovato unveils her steamiest music video yet with 'Cool for the Summer'|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a659853/demi-lovato-unveils-her-steamiest-music-video-yet-with-cool-for-the-summer.html#~pjibjIfb7DzAW7|publisher=Digital Spy|accessdate=2015-07-23|date=2015-07-23|archive-date=2015-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151026175741/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a659853/demi-lovato-unveils-her-steamiest-music-video-yet-with-cool-for-the-summer.html#~pjibjIfb7DzAW7|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[尼龙|Nylon]]》的海登·曼德斯（{{lang|en|Hayden Manders}}）称视频“不会令人失望，但它有些地方忘记打标记”，解释称：“一首关于同性试验的歌曲的录影带没有提到其主题是很奇怪的。你不得不注意歌词来了解基本信息，因为视频回避了这一点<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Manders|first1=Hayden|title=demi lovato's queer "cool for the summer" song gets a non-queer video|url=http://www.nylon.com/articles/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer-music-video|magazine=Nylon|accessdate=2015-07-23|date=2015-07-23|journal=|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303192312/http://www.nylon.com/articles/demi-lovato-cool-for-the-summer-music-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《纽约》杂志的迪伊·洛基称它是“黛米有史以来在性感上最开放的录影带，释放去强有力的信息”<ref name="vulture1"/>。录影带于2015年10月录到超过1亿的点击率，成为洛瓦托第九部获[[VEVO#VEVO認證獎|Vevo认证]]的短片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vevo.com/watch/demi-lovato/cool-for-the-summer-%28official-video%29/USH5V1522462|title=Cool for the Summer (Official Video) - Demi Lovato|work=Vevo|accessdate=2015-11-20|archive-date=2018-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180606115419/https://www.vevo.com/watch/demi-lovato/cool-for-the-summer-(official-video)/USH5V1522462|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

