歌曲共获得两项提名。2015年8月，歌曲在[[2015年青少年选择奖|青少年选择奖]]上被提名夏季选择歌曲奖（{{lang|en|Choice Summer Song}}）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/08/16/teen-choice-awards-winners-2015-tca-winner-list|last=Steiner|first=Amanda|title=Teen Choice Awards 2015: See the full list of winners!|publisher=E! Online|date=2015-08-16|accessdate=2015-08-19|archive-date=2015-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150817151434/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/08/16/teen-choice-awards-winners-2015-tca-winner-list|dead-url=no}}</ref>，还在[[2015年MTV音乐录影带大奖|MTV音乐录影带大奖]]上被提名为夏日歌曲（{{lang|en|Song of Summer}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2243857/vma-song-of-the-summer-category/|title=There’s A New VMA Category, And You Need To Start Voting Now|publisher=[[MTV|MTV]]|accessdate=2015-08-20|date=2015-08-18|archive-date=2015-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904113637/http://www.mtv.com/news/2243857/vma-song-of-the-summer-category/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2016年4月27日举行的2016年[[美国作曲家、作家和发行商协会|ASCAP流行音乐奖]]上，歌曲荣膺2015年最热门歌曲之一奖<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ascap.com/eventsawards/awards/popawards/2016/awards-home|title=2016 ASCAP Pop Music Awards|publisher=American Society of Composers, Authors and Publishers|accessdate=2016-04-29|archive-date=2017-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223050122/https://www.ascap.com/news-events/awards/2016/pop-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

